title: Fineliner v1.5.0 - Responsive Portfolio WordPress Theme
description:
Fineliner is a beautiful and clean responsive WordPress theme that is perfectly suitable for building any portfolio or business websites. The theme comes with 6 accent colors and you can adjust more using Style Customizer module. It also comes with a powerful page builder powered by Visual Composer plugin. Another premium LayerSlider plugin for managing wonderful sliders is also included. The theme already supports WPML plugin and you can easily use it for creating the multilingual site. Lastly, want to setup your own shop? You can go ahead using WooCommerce plugin with the theme.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/fineliner-responsive-portfolio-wordpress-theme/6363903

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
